Document: WebRTCPeerConnectionExtension
Path: godot/classes/class_webrtcpeerconnectionextension.rst
Summary: Base class for WebRTC peer connection implementations.

Inherits: Object < Object

This class is the base for all WebRTC peer connection implementations. It defines the core API for establishing and managing peer-to-peer connections using the WebRTC protocol. You typically won't interact with this class directly, but rather with its concrete implementations like WebRTCPeerConnection.

Key Rule: This class serves as an abstract base class and cannot be instantiated directly. Use its derived classes for actual WebRTC functionality.
